ZH: 倘若你明天有时间，我们可以一起去看电影。
EN: If you have time tomorrow, we can go watch a movie together.

ZH: 倘若天气好，我会和朋友去爬山。
EN: If the weather is good, I will go hiking with my friends.

ZH: 倘若你不跟我道歉，我们就不能继续做朋友了。
EN: If you don't apologize to me, we can't be friends anymore.

ZH: 倘若我有足够的经验，我会自己开发一个软件。
EN: If I have enough experience, I will develop a software on my own.

ZH: 倘若他不努力学习，就无法通过考试。
EN: If he doesn't study hard, he won't be able to pass the exam.

ZH: 倘若我有机会，我会去旅行世界各地。
EN: If I have the opportunity, I will travel around the world.

ZH: 倘若你买了这个衣服后悔了，可以退货吗？
EN: If you regret buying this dress, can you return it?

ZH: 倘若你不想吃这道菜，我可以给你换一份。
EN: If you don't want to eat this dish, I can get you a different one.

ZH: 倘若他改变了态度，我们可以考虑给他一个机会。
EN: If he changes his attitude, we can consider giving him a chance.

ZH: 倘若你有更好的建议，欢迎提出来。
EN: If you have better suggestions, please feel free to propose them.

ZH: 倘若你不来接我，我只能自己回家了。
EN: If you don't come to pick me up, I will have to go home by myself.

ZH: 倘若这个电影票涨价了，我就不去了。
EN: If the price of this movie ticket increases, I won't go.

ZH: 倘若你迟到了，我们就会错过开场。
EN: If you are late, we will miss the beginning.

ZH: 倘若你不喜欢这首歌，我可以给你换一首。
EN: If you don't like this song, I can play a different one for you.

ZH: 倘若你需要帮助，随时找我。
EN: If you need help, feel free to reach out to me.

ZH: 倘若你把这样做成习惯，你会收获更多成功。
EN: If you make this a habit, you will achieve more success.

ZH: 倘若你不明白，可以再问一遍。
EN: If you don't understand, you can ask again.

ZH: 倘若你不穿合适的鞋子，容易受伤。
EN: If you don't wear proper shoes, you are more prone to injuries.

ZH: 倘若你能集中注意力，你会解决这个问题的。
EN: If you can focus your attention, you will solve this problem.

ZH: 倘若你不放弃，就还有机会成功。
EN: If you don't give up, there is still a chance for success.
